I'm with comwilson on the numbering.

If you have a main object and a secondary product or manifestation I can see the main one being SCP-XXX and the extras XXX-1 to whatever. But certain things don't have a main component so much as they have distinct and dependent parts, like this one. So I think it's valid to have 382-1 and 382-2 rather than an original 382. 382 just represents everything under containment in this case.







